# ignore EVERYTHING
/*

# just kidding - include allow list for bare miniumum files needed to run/read
!/.github/
!/.gitignore
!/ATTRIBUTION.md
!/CHANGELOG.md
!/LICENSES.md
!/README.md
!/images/
!/pipeline/
!/engine/

# Ignore generated published local-only artifacts
# (engine/planet/ baked voxel chunks ARE published on purpose so a fresh clone runs out of the box — see README. Regenerate via pipeline/src/export.py.)
engine/.godot/
engine/export_presets.cfg
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.pyo
**/.pytest_cache/
**/*.egg-info/
**/.venv/
**/venv/
